<section class="about-section" id="about">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="about-content reveal">
      <div class="section-label">About</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">I'm Irene. I build websites<br>for contractors.</h2>
      <p>I'll be honest with you: I'm not a big marketing agency. I'm not going to promise you'll be on the first page of Google in 30 days. Anyone who tells you that is lying.</p>
      <p>What I am is someone who's watched too many contractors get ripped off by lead generation companies and overpriced marketing agencies. I started Sites On Call because I believe there's a better way — building something you actually own instead of renting your customers from Angi.</p>
      <p>I'm based here in North Alabama. When you work with me, you're working with me — not getting handed off to some account manager who doesn't know your name. I answer my own phone and I actually care whether your business grows.</p>
      <p>This is still a new business. I'm not going to pretend I have 500 clients and a fancy office. But I know websites, I know SEO, and I know how to help contractors stop throwing money at lead services that don't work.</p>
      <p><strong>Skeptical?</strong> Good. You should be. That's exactly the kind of contractor I want to work with.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="faq">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center">
